defaultThe point here is that the
default highly
default uneven impact of the ’bedroom tax’ 
defaulthas largely
default been overlooked.  Yet it is increasingly leading to widespread distress in some of the most disadvantaged communities in Britain.  According to reports to Alliance na
defaulttional meetings
default, the ‘bedroom tax’ is leading to a sharp rise in rent arrears, to high le
