default be misleading
default to take the housing-related benefit changes out of their wider context.
default  Changes to
default 
defaultincapacity and disability benefits, 
defaultto 
defaulttax credits and 
defaultto 
defaultChild B
defaultenefit
default are underway at the same time
default, and 
defaultin several cases are
default substantially larger in terms
default of their financial impact.  The effect is that
default several d
defaultifferent elements to the
default welfare reform package impact simultaneously on the same households and individuals.
